metadata.name: Summer Green
metadata.description:
「涼しいところへ来たつもりだったが、ここでも夏は暑かった。汗をかいて立ち止まる私をよそに、周りの緑はたおやかに、しなやかに揺れていた」


“I thought I had come to a cooler place, but Summer was still hot even here.  I was so sweaty that I stopped. On the other hand, the greenery around me was swayed gracefully and flexibly. ”


新潟県長岡市  
Nagaoka, Niigata
